Known JDT/Debug deficiency they were supposed to react against earlier this 
week. 

JDT/Core complains in the .log, but silently fixes up things internally (though 
it should not have to, and thus issues this complaint).

Fixed. We no longer use "null", but can use the empty path.

*** This bug has been marked as a duplicate of 38531 ***
